{"tid":797033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【顫抖吧】曼聯上次頭3場輸2場　結果...","createTime":"2018-08-28T07:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T08:14:08.000Z","uid":13797,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b64e8708192c03f409775418c30145927d00d624","tid":797033,"uid":13797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"曼聯今季頭3場聯賽1勝2負，表現令球迷失望，睇番「紅魔鬼」對上一次喺頭3輪聯額2次落敗，原來已經要數到1992/93球季，亦即係第1季英超聯賽。當年曼聯喺開鑼戰作客1比2輸畀錫周三，次後返主場再吞愛華頓3蛋，去到第3場先至1比1打和葉士域治「止血」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然個頭開得差，不過「紅魔鬼」當年有簡當東拿加盟實力強勁，最終佢哋以10分差距拋棄阿士東維拉成功封王，象徵「曼聯王朝」正式展開。"},{"pid":"278f6093099e2465dcc0d6e68ada6966de54b591","tid":797033,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c759fb12f7969e9d7697444797d877ed2d30da","tid":797033,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"簡當東拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e85a45efa272cb9cb187a779a438ea0766a2d6d","tid":797033,"uid":160934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"曼聯又成最大贏家"},{"pid":"28099ee19afa30373f54946baa8a54093f13042e","tid":797033,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e31245988af4b339fe7878f6bd8cc95c47ade4","tid":797033,"uid":79711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"全能到仆街起碼高簡東拿一班波<br />\n曼今季又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\